snippet.textDisplay:
For all those who are criticising Seyonee's CS version. 

It is very easy to comment. Look at the arrangement of the music. Salman did nothing with that. His solo was great. CS is all about experiment. They are not here to make it perfect like original. If you need to listen original one, just go and listen that, as it is already available for you to listen. Yes, Rahat's vocal has some ups and down, and Yes, Ali Azmat must have done more justice. But, I guess most of you not aware that he was requested by Salman and CS management for that. But for his arrogance to not perform with Salman, could not make this happen. Salman time and again approached him for collaboration, but he refused all the time. 
In the end, Just listen this fresh fusion and support Pak Music.
